title: Superstar: The Karen Carpenter Story (Todd Haynes) DivX
description:
Karen Carpenter&#039;s battle with anorexia nervosa and the cultural influence of the Carpenters in the 70s. 

Squashed by the Carpenter estate this film is all but impossible to see. I think it has less to do with "unauthorized" use of Carpenter songs then the fact that Karen&#039;s family comes across as monsters and largely responsible for her death.
All of the parts are played out by Ken and Barbie dolls.
